{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Niepolomice?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Till-- till they make Niepolomice a judenrein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, everybody from these vicinities around Niepolomice has to, after this certain date, find themselves in Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wieliczka, this is a little town 12 kilometers from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The famous salt mine was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe you've heard about there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here, after that day, anybody who finds himself outside the line where they say is going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the way they did it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, they round up all Wieliczka, and the deportations start.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And here, the first time, what you-- you really saw what the Germans are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were tearing at pieces children, babies-- throwing out through the windows, babies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Winding them up-- grab them by the leg, and turn them around and through the window, out, and shot them in the air.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Old people-- two Germans, one-- one-- one picked up by leg, the other one by-- no.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By the neck or by the hand, and throw them, you know, on the truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Little-- they were still-- everybody was still alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Like a sack of potatoes on the truck, on the truck, one on the top of the other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I stood up there, and I said, my God.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a beautiful, hot day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Is there a God, is what they say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He is up there, and he looks on those things, what they do to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No, there's no God.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If he could be up there and just look at it and not to do anything-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people were dying from thirst.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They used to go out way before three days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in the meantime, they were going all over the town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "People were hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
